        "subject": "LUS-6319 migrate: remove source object after migrate",
        "message": "LUS-6319 migrate: remove source object after migrate\n\nDon't link a migrating object into PENDING dir, it causes an FS\ncorruption and the object will not be unlinked until target restart.\n\nTest to check that is added.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <c17817@cray.com>\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\nChange-Id: Ie06c805396bb212d1447344ccd509d2e90692033\n"
